  <summary date="2015-01-14T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Moving Obstructed Trains In-between Openings Now (MOTION) Act

Allows railroad employees to remain or go on duty for a period in excess of the limitations established under hours-of-service requirements to the extent necessary to clear a blockage of vehicular traffic at a grade crossing.</summary>
